\\n  A2 第一幕故事包 wrong_number_act1 → data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/\\n     （story.conf.json + cards/*.s-card.json + canvas.layout.json）\\n\\n阶段 B · 管道接通（列表 + 读写）+ 同步清 mock\\n  B [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":30,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_fc6ff9d0-95c8-47b2-96ef-5b979648918\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/项目第三步计划执行索引.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\n# Studio V2.0 · 项目第三步计划执行索引（gbx / general-batch-exe）\\n# 用法：node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile <本文件> --workdir <仓库根> [--dry-run]\\n# 本轮目标：真实业务接线（非 mock 模拟）；接通后立刻删对应 mock；第一幕 wrong_number_act1；编辑器读写+接线\\nbatch_size: 1\\nmax_rounds: 80\\nmax_fix_attempts: 5\\nmax_ineffective_fixes: 2\\nstop_on_fail: true\\ngroup: order\\n\\nverify_default:\\n  - npm run quality:studio\\n\\nread_first:\\n  - AGENTS.md\\n  - .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-boundaries.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/testing-and-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc\\n  - docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/第三步需求.md\\n  - docs/AI/00-Studio-V2代码事实索引.md\\n  - docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md\\n  - docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":31,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_e48de142-768e-40fb-b971-267f2d9ace3\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"V2-T3-8\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"tool_e48de142-768e-40fb-b971-267f2d9ace3\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"V2-T3-8\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"conten