ality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc\\n  - docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/第三步需求.md\\n  - docs/AI/00-Studio-V2代码事实索引.md\\n  - docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md\\n  - docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":31,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_e48de142-768e-40fb-b971-267f2d9ace3\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"V2-T3-8\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"tool_e48de142-768e-40fb-b971-267f2d9ace3\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"V2-T3-8\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"content\":{\"matches\":[{\"file\":\"./.ai-workflow-v2-step3/prompts/agent-1784712859758.log\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":1,\"content\":\"[gbx] ▶ executor:V2-T3-8 start cmd=cursor-agent cwd=/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":12,\"content\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_call\\\",\\\"subtype\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"call_id\\\":\\\"tool_2148a945-cc47-45c2-a403-f60e053165b\\\",\\\"tool_call\\\":{\\\"readToolCall\\\":{\\\"args\\\":{\\\"path\\\":\\\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-step3/promp [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_ca4bfb80-0d15-4a6d-b48d-1f00cb961ee\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/07-已知边界与下一步候选.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# 已知边界与下一步候选（代码事实）\\n\\n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-5 后：角色/玩家真源 + 故事包 BFF 已接通）。  \\n> 「站稳」指：角色/玩家 CRUD 可落盘刷新仍在；故事包可经 `/api/stories` 整包读写；不等于列表/编辑器 UI 已切盘或 Host 闭环完成。\\n\\n## 1. 故意未做 / 尚未做\\n\\n| 项