{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_0054a23f-5fb3-4d25-96be-4b5a3ab2c6b","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/03-故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗.md","limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗（代码事实）\n\n> 对照：`apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/**` + `bis/pageBis/storyEditor/**`。  \n> UI 向导需求：[02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿](../../AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿.md)。  \n> Effect 面板细化：[细化修改7_需求](../../AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改7_需求.md)。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-8：打开读盘 + 整包保存 + 编辑接线落盘）。\n\n## 1. 壳层结构（认知地图）\n\n```text\nStoryEditorShell\n  ├ StoryEditorTopBar          # chapterTitle 等；保存 → saveStoryPackage_bis\n  ├ StoryEditorCanvasLayer     # React Flow 舞台\n  │    └ StoryCanvasStage / useStoryCanvasGraph\n  ├ FloatingPanelShell         # 属性浮窗（可拖、粘性头尾）\n  │    ├ NodePropertyForm | ChapterPropertyForm\n  │    └ ExitListEditor → ExitEffectsList → ExitEffectPanel\n  ├ BottomToolBar              # placement：CallCard / chapter_end …\n  └ library floats             # 包配置 / 资源挑选等\n```\n\n会话态：节点/边在 `useStoryCanvasGraph` 的 React state；**顶栏保存**经 `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 `data/storis-packages`。\n\n## 2. 节点种类\n\n| React Flow type | data 投影 | 作用 |\n|-----------------|-----------|------|\n| `callCard` | `EditorCallCardProjection` | 通话合同卡 |\n| `chapter` | `EditorChapterNodeData` | `chapter_start` / `chapter_end` |\n| `characterAnchor` | `CharacterAnchorNodeData` | 左侧角色锚点；role handle |\n\n另有轻量 dock 节点（action / commentGroup）：可放置，但属性浮窗策略与 CallCard 分离（见 dock 工厂）。\n\n## 3. 边种类\n\n| edgeKind | 视觉意图 | 真源 |\n|----------|----------|------|\n| `story` | 章节/出口流转（实线） | layout.edges + 会话内连线 |\n| `role` | 卡 → 锚点归属（灰点线） | `ROLE_EDGE_STYLE` |\n| `effect` | attach/unmount（绿虚线等） | `effectEdgeSync.ts` 与 `exit.effects[]` 双向 |\n\n效果边 id：`effect_${sourceNodeId}_${exitId}_${effectId}`，须与 layout 种子边一致以便 reconcile 幂等。\n\n## 4. 选中与属性浮窗（铁律级行为）\n\n- **仅单选**节点打开属性浮窗：`storyCanvasSelection.ts` 中 `params.nodes.length === 1`。  \n- **框选多节点不得开浮窗**（曾出岔子，见 [06](./06-过程岔子与纠正记录.md)）。  \n- `selectionKind`：`callCard` | `chapter`；锚点走角色 FormModal，不是 CallCard 浮窗。  \n- 防御：`toolPolicy?.mode ?? \"\"` 等，避免缺字段炸表单。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":72,"fileSize":3710,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/03-故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_0054a23f-5fb3-4d25-96be-4b5a3ab2c6b","startedAtMs":"1784713061776","completedAtMs":"1784713061975"},"model_call_id":"d89841fd-457a-49fa-8413-4e377e0e924f-7-6wsv","session_id":"8e98fde1-c0c8-4bb2-b54f-b1d682a97d99","timestamp_ms":1784713061786}
